{"tid":122102,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"嘈到訓唔到","createTime":"2017-02-15T18:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T00:55:58.000Z","uid":70069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d95eb866530ed748d81ba3147fd3e9e192739fa2","tid":122102,"uid":70069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T18:33:24.000Z","msg":"由細到大同家姐同房 最近佢每晚都傾電話傾幾個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  內容無興趣刻意去聽 但都會聽得出語氣似係拍拖或者同人曖昧(因為平時佢從來唔會咁輕聲細語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n呢個星期我每晚都因為咁訓唔著 <br />\n因為我一熄燈佢就以為我訓左佢就愈講愈興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我唔反對拍拖亦唔反對講電話 但可唔可以係夜晚阻住我訓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係大家覺得我先係有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd288b3db0a017098f1dc7318cec7ae3fcd534b4","tid":122102,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T18:37:00.000Z","msg":"你個名係咪為佢而改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242382691f21ecd74fb5deb55e34ddec040e798f","tid":122102,"uid":29371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T18:37:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個名係咪為佢而改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6e7819cf9d9b93b8a76be6ebfa521912dd3c1a","tid":122102,"uid":70069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T18:38:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個名係咪為佢而改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"